        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "heads of the house of their fathers, mighty men of valour; principal men in their tribe and families, and of great courage: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and were reckoned by their genealogies twenty and two thousand and thirty and four; who sprung from these men. ",
